:57:29.000Z","msg":"妹仔又唔敢出聲喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/105707_91b95c349c0cd37ab220e2ffba4389ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F105707_91b95c349c0cd37ab220e2ffba4389ac.png&h=a2004d57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bb76d92336677447d7203868545c9491f80f417","tid":681764,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"樓主港豬到呢"},{"pid":"8a12502c92fdf403e1c6d7756f6e3c2c245bb398","tid":681764,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"你係咪新移民"},{"pid":"ca3b12e3af056a1dbb8d7999290bc0ba6f9156b4","tid":681764,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6f6102e44b3dd2f5aca1c70091a40a577083645","tid":681764,"uid":12408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"自從誠品開左都淨係會去誠品買書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又可以順手睇下精品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"好遠😞"},{"pid":"bb1dfbb50da56516ca665b14d18926222bd7365a","tid":681764,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"無行三中商好耐<br />\n除左工具書根本無野好買"},{"pid":"2db0a0fb952d9eca514c5559ff49ff27bb3b212a","tid":681764,"uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"香港獨立書店地圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1cOvIGzrqIiD6_XGUtcShdL3uW6Q&amp;ll=22.37111055153268%2C113.88821484999994&amp;z=10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1cOvIGzrqIiD6_XGUtcShdL3uW6Q%26ll%3D22.37111055153268%252C113.88821484999994%26z%3D10&d=LJrlrQnCPRTkRTA%2FSLTgpTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=dc5ff1eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1cOvIGzrqIiD6_XGUtcShdL3uW6Q&amp;ll=22.37111055153268%2C113.88821484999994&amp;z=10</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為推動文化的重要場所，書店連結著生活空間和書本世界。<br />\n<br />\n然而踏入 2015 ，香港似乎無論生活空間和書本世界都面臨龐大壓力。才剛過一季，IFC 的 Dymocks、時代廣場的 Page One，都已相繼關門大吉。連海外連鎖書店也不敵年年飆升的租金，更何況自家經營的小店？旺角一帶的樓上書店也風聲鶴唳，旺角博學軒倒下，榆林書店二合為一。<br />\n<br />\n書愈來愈難賣，但有人堅持愈難愈要賣。有從業員依然審慎樂觀：不是擔心沒有人買，只怕租金漲得太快。<br />\n<br />\n最近多本有關雨傘運動的書籍，遭三聯、中華、商務書局三大中資書店冷待，「三中商」積極推銷一批歪曲佔領運動的書籍，叫市民再次注意到「三中商」壟斷香港書籍零售市場及政治審查的情況。文化界紛紛為獨立出版和書店站台，浸會大學社會工作系講師邵家臻直言：「獨立出版社很慘，樓上書店要撐。」<br />\n<br />\n面對「三中商」封殺和租金壓力，支持獨立書店，需要集體行動。《立場新聞》整理香港獨立書店最新資料，如有遺漏、錯誤、過時，請讀者指正， 我們會持續更新。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%2F&d=LJrlrQnCPRTkRTA%2FSLTgpTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b2c1453a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%2F&h=45a338a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96/</a><br />\n<br />\n田園書屋<br />\n解憂舊書店<br />\n樂文書店<br />\n樂活書緣<br />\n艺鵠<br />\n序言書室<br />\nMCCM CREATIONS<br />\n小息書店<br />\n地攤<br />\n發條貓<br />\n人民公社<br />\n向日葵出版社<br />\n陳湘記書局（旺角）<br />\n森記圖書公司<br />\n香港上海印書館<br />\n精神書局（北角）<br />\n精神書局（西環）<br />\n新亞書店<br />\n銅鑼灣書店<br />\n香港青年出版社<br />\n陳湘記書局（灣仔）<br />\n溢記舊書<br />\n新天書業<br />\n神州舊書文玩有限公司<br />\n春藤書坊<br />\n上書局<br />\nBooks &amp; Co.<br />\n校友書局<br />\n智源書局有限公司（日本圖書中心）<br />\n開益書店<br />\nParenth&egrave;se<br />\n國風堂書屋<br />\nImprint Bookshop<br />\n博雅小書店<br />\n梅馨書舍<br />\nBOOKSMART<br />\n我的書房<br />\n樂文<br />\n榆林書店<br />\n文苑書店<br />\n讀書人書店<br />\n樂文書店（銅鑼灣店）<br />\n佛哲書舍（太子）<br />\n佛哲書舍（元